                            <h2>QGraphics</h2>
                            <p>I built this library to provide a quick way to build graphical programs using openGL in windows. It is built on QMaths 
                                and has features to create a wide variety of built-in 3D shapes, lighting and materials, and even allows importing FBX models
                                created in Blender.
                            </p>
                            <p>This covers everything needed for a simple 3D graphics program, including mouse and keyboard input, camera controls and the ability
                                to precisely move, rotate or scale objects.
                            </p>
