                            <p>It features 3D movement, with each piece visibly lifting off the board, and a shadow effect underneath. It also uses multiple materials
                                for the pieces to indicate kings and selected pieces.</p>
                            <p>The repo can be found <a href="https://github.com/shawrie777/Draughts">here.</a></p>
