                            <p>Inspired by <a href="https://www.wolframalpha.com/">Wolfram Alpha</a>, I'm building this with the intention of it being 
                            able to solve as many equations as possible.</p>
                            <p>It uses regular expressions to understand the users input and creates a set of nested expressions to prioritise its order
                                of operations. It then works from the deepest nested layer outwards to find a solution. This is still a work in progress.
                            </p>
